                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold">Guru BK</h4>
                    <p class="text-emerald-300 text-sm mt-2">Pendidik profesional di sekolah & madrasah.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center group">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-emerald-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:bg-emerald-500 transition border border-emerald-700">
